35
00:03:17,114 --> 00:03:18,782
AND AGAIN, IT WAS
THE THREE NEW GUNDAMS

36
00:03:18,782 --> 00:03:20,409
THAT PERFORMED
THE ATTACK.

37
00:03:20,409 --> 00:03:23,370
MR. PRESIDENT...THE
INTERVENTIONS OF THE NEW MODELS

38
00:03:23,370 --> 00:03:26,415
ARE CLEARLY DIFFERENT IN NATURE
FROM THE PREVIOUS ONES.

39
00:03:26,415 --> 00:03:29,668
DARING TO COME TOGETHER IN A
LARGE JOINT MILITARY EXERCISE

40
00:03:29,668 --> 00:03:32,129
MUST HAVE BROUGHT DOWN THE
WRATH OF THE GUNDAMS.

41
00:03:32,129 --> 00:03:35,715
Official #2C:
THERE IS NO WAY WE CAN DEAL WITH
CELESTIAL BEING ON OUR OWN.

42
00:03:35,715 --> 00:03:38,468
OBVIOUSLY, WE NEED TO STRENGTHEN
OUR TIES WITH THE OTHER BLOCS.

43
00:03:38,468 --> 00:03:40,512
AND YOU THINK THAT WILL
HELP US DEFEAT THE GUNDAMS?

44
00:03:40,512 --> 00:03:42,556
Official #2A:
WELL THEN WHAT DO
YOU SUGGEST WE DO?

45
00:03:44,099 --> 00:03:47,436
IS THERE NOTHING WE
CAN DO TO STOP THEM?

46
00:03:47,436 --> 00:03:48,770
Peries:
COLONEL...

47
00:03:48,770 --> 00:03:50,522
DO YOU THINK THE GUNDAMS
WILL LAUNCH AN ATTACK ON US

48
00:03:50,522 --> 00:03:51,898
UP HERE AS WELL?

49
00:03:51,898 --> 00:03:53,650
THAT IS A POSSIBILITY.

50
00:03:53,650 --> 00:03:56,069
I'D EXPECT THEM TO CONTINUE
SUCH ACTIONS

51
00:03:56,069 --> 00:03:57,779
IF THEIR GOAL
IS TO DESTROY THE WORLD.

52
00:04:00,699 --> 00:04:03,410
YOU DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT THE NEW GUNDAMS?

53
00:04:03,410 --> 00:04:05,370
EVEN YOU, AN OBSERVER?

54
00:04:05,370 --> 00:04:07,789
MY INFORMATION IS LIMITED

55
00:04:07,789 --> 00:04:10,500
ACCORDING TO MY ACCESS
LEVEL AS SET BY VEDA.

56
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:13,003
THEIR TEAM NAME IS
TRINITY.

57
00:04:13,003 --> 00:04:15,589
THEIR MACHINES ARE
CALLED GUNDAM THRONES.

58
00:04:15,589 --> 00:04:18,300
AND THAT'S AS MUCH AS
I KNOW ABOUT THEM.

59
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:20,760
THIS IS JUST MY
PERSONAL OPINION...

60
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:23,388
BUT I THINK THEIR
ACTIONS ARE SOMEWHAT EXTREME.

61
00:04:23,388 --> 00:04:24,681
SO TELL ME THEN,

62
00:04:24,681 --> 00:04:26,475
DO YOU BELIEVE
THAT THE EXISTENCE

63
00:04:26,475 --> 00:04:28,602
OF THE TRINITYS IS ALSO
PART OF OUR ORIGINAL PLAN?

64
00:04:28,602 --> 00:04:31,730
THAT'S A REASONABLE CONCLUSION
GIVEN THE FACTS.

65
00:04:31,730 --> 00:04:34,274
AFTER ALL, THEY ARE IN
POSSESSION

66
00:04:34,274 --> 00:04:36,318
OF MOBILE
WEAPONS CALLED GUNDAMS.

67
00:04:37,986 --> 00:04:39,154
Ian:
ABOUT THOSE THRONES...

68
00:04:39,154 --> 00:04:41,072
THEIR SYSTEMS
AND ARMOR

69
00:04:41,072 --> 00:04:43,158
USE THE SAME TECHNOLOGY
THAT OURS DO.

70
00:04:43,158 --> 00:04:44,910
SO THEY'RE
OF THE SAME TYPE.

71
00:04:44,910 --> 00:04:47,162
BUT THEIR GN DRIVES
ARE DIFFERENT.

72
00:04:47,162 --> 00:04:49,873
THEIR SOLAR REACTORS
ARE DIFFERENT?

73
00:04:49,873 --> 00:04:51,833
WELL, THEY'RE
FUNCTIONALLY IDENTICAL...

74
00:04:51,833 --> 00:04:54,628
BUT THE REACTOR CORE
DOESN'T USE A TD BLANKET.

75
00:04:54,628 --> 00:04:57,631
THUS THE OPERATING TIME OF
THE DRIVE ITSELF IS LIMITED.

76
00:04:57,631 --> 00:05:00,342
Ian:
IN OTHER WORDS, THESE ARE
PSEUDO SOLAR REACTORS.

77
00:05:00,967 --> 00:05:03,762
SO, THIS IS A CASE WHERE
SOMEONE STOLE CELESTIAL BEING'S

78
00:05:03,762 --> 00:05:05,680
TECHNOLOGY AND THEN BUILT
THEIR OWN GUNDAMS?

79
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,015
HOW COULD THAT HAPPEN?

80
00:05:07,015 --> 00:05:09,184
THE BLUEPRINTS FOR THE
SOLAR REACTORS

81
00:05:09,184 --> 00:05:11,353
CAN ONLY BE FOUND
IN VEDA'S DATABANKS.

82
00:05:11,353 --> 00:05:12,479
WHICH MEANS...

83
00:05:12,479 --> 00:05:13,814
ARE YOU SAYING
SOMEONE

84
00:05:13,814 --> 00:05:15,232
ACTUALLY HACKED
THEIR WAY INTO VEDA?

85
00:05:15,232 --> 00:05:16,441
THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE!

86
00:05:16,441 --> 00:05:17,567
CHRIS...

87
00:05:17,567 --> 00:05:19,861
THERE'S NO SUCH THING
AS AN ABSOLUTE.

88
00:05:19,861 --> 00:05:22,030
EVEN IF IT WAS TRUE...

89
00:05:22,030 --> 00:05:24,991
IT TAKES QUITE A LOT OF TIME TO
BUILD A SOLAR REACTOR.

90
00:05:24,991 --> 00:05:27,702
WELL, AT THE VERY LEAST, IT
MEANS WE HAVE A TRAITOR

91
00:05:27,702 --> 00:05:29,204
SOMEWHERE IN THE
ORGANIZATION.

92
00:05:30,163 --> 00:05:31,540
SO IT WOULD SEEM.

93
00:05:36,711 --> 00:05:41,132
(Thinking):
LEVEL THREE CLEAR.
LEVEL FOUR. LEVEL FIVE.

94
00:05:41,132 --> 00:05:42,133
(Gasps)

95
00:05:43,885 --> 00:05:47,639
SOME OF THE DATA FROM LEVEL
SEVEN HAS BEEN ALTERED.

96
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:49,516
I WONDER WHAT
THIS DATA COVERS...

97
00:05:50,642 --> 00:05:52,060
(Alarm sounds)

98
00:05:52,060 --> 00:05:53,436
I'VE BEEN REJECTED?

99
00:05:53,436 --> 00:05:56,690
BUT IT'S ME! HOW COULD
I BE DENIED ACCESS?

100
00:05:57,482 --> 00:05:59,901
(Tieria thinking):
VEDA... WHAT IS GOING ON HERE?

101
00:06:03,697 --> 00:06:05,407
SO... WHAT DO WE
DO NOW?

102
00:06:05,407 --> 00:06:07,284
LOOK, IF THE WORLD
ACTUALLY THINKS

103
00:06:07,284 --> 00:06:09,703
THAT WE'RE BROTHERS IN
ARMS WITH TEAM TRINITY,

104
00:06:09,703 --> 00:06:12,289
THEN IT WOULD BE DANGEROUS TO
GO ON ANY MISSIONS RIGHT NOW.

105
00:06:12,289 --> 00:06:14,416
WE HAVE TO KEEP
AN EYE ON THEM WHILE WE LEARN

106
00:06:14,416 --> 00:06:15,875
AS MUCH AS WE CAN
ABOUT THEM...

107
00:06:15,875 --> 00:06:17,502
THEN WE CAN
DEVISE A RESPONSE.

108
00:06:17,502 --> 00:06:19,504
SOUNDS LIKE A JOB
FOR WANG LIU MEI.

109
00:06:22,716 --> 00:06:25,510
MISTRESS, THE PTOLEMAOIS
SENT US THE BIOMETRIC DATA

110
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:27,596
THEY GATHERED
ON THE TRINITY PILOTS...

111
00:06:27,596 --> 00:06:29,889
BUT WE HAVEN'T FOUND ANY
MATCHING INDIVIDUALS.

112
00:06:29,889 --> 00:06:31,725
REDOUBLE YOUR EFFORTS,
PLEASE.

113
00:06:31,725 --> 00:06:33,727
AS YOU WISH, MISTRESS.

114
00:06:35,979 --> 00:06:39,232
THE TRINITYS' METHODS ARE
CERTAINLY RECKLESS...

115
00:06:39,232 --> 00:06:42,235
BUT IF THE WORLD
CHANGES AS A RESULT...

116
00:06:42,694 --> 00:06:44,112
(Whoosh)

117
00:06:48,074 --> 00:06:50,952
(Birds chirping)

118
00:06:52,621 --> 00:06:54,664
Graham:
HOWARD MASON...

119
00:06:54,664 --> 00:06:56,166
HOWARD HAD
NOTHING BUT

120
00:06:56,166 --> 00:06:58,043
THE GREATEST RESPECT
FOR YOU, CAPTAIN.

121
00:06:58,043 --> 00:07:00,587
HE BELIEVED THAT
THE FLAG WAS CHOSEN

122
00:07:00,587 --> 00:07:02,422
TO BE OUR NEXT‐GENERATION
MOBILE SUIT...

123
00:07:02,422 --> 00:07:05,050
BECAUSE OF YOUR
EFFORTS AS A TEST PILOT, SIR.

124
00:07:06,217 --> 00:07:08,219
THE ONLY REASON I ACCEPTED
THE ASSIGNMENT

125
00:07:08,219 --> 00:07:09,929
TO BE THE FLAG'S
TEST PILOT WAS BECAUSE

126
00:07:09,929 --> 00:07:11,848
I THOUGHT IT WAS THE BEST.

127
00:07:11,848 --> 00:07:14,893
AND THEN...IN THAT MOCK
BATTLE DURING TESTING...

128
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:18,021
THAT WAS AN UNFORTUNATE
ACCIDENT, SIR!

129
00:07:20,482 --> 00:07:23,485
CAPTAIN...HOWARD SAID
SOMETHING TO ME ONCE:

130
00:07:23,485 --> 00:07:25,153
"IT'S THANKS
TO THE CAPTAIN

131
00:07:25,153 --> 00:07:27,781
"THAT I WAS ABLE TO
BECOME A FLAG FIGHTER!

132
00:07:27,781 --> 00:07:31,493
"AND NOW I GET THE CHANCE TO
FLY THE SKIES WITH HIM..."

133
00:07:31,493 --> 00:07:32,827
I SEE.

134
00:07:32,827 --> 00:07:34,954
SOUNDS LIKE HE LOVED
THE FLAG...

135
00:07:34,954 --> 00:07:36,289
EVEN MORE THAN I DID.

136
00:07:37,165 --> 00:07:38,166
(Sighs)

137
00:07:40,085 --> 00:07:43,088
REST EASY, HOWARD MASON,
FOR I SWEAR THIS:

138
00:07:43,088 --> 00:07:45,590
I, GRAHAM AKER,
WILL USE A FLAG

139
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:47,509
WHEN I FINALLY
DEFEAT THE GUNDAMS!

140
00:07:49,678 --> 00:07:50,679
(Grunts)

141
00:07:56,309 --> 00:07:57,977
(People talking)

142
00:07:57,977 --> 00:07:59,896
SORRY FOR MAKING YOU COME
ALL THE WAY OUT HERE.

143
00:07:59,896 --> 00:08:02,065
WELL, IT'S BETTER
THAN MEETING NEAR THE BASE.

144
00:08:02,065 --> 00:08:04,109
MORE IMPORTANTLY,
WHERE'S MY CASH?

145
00:08:06,403 --> 00:08:07,654
SHOOT.

146
00:08:07,654 --> 00:08:10,532
I HEARD YOU WERE IN THAT BIG
MILITARY EXERCISE...

147
00:08:10,532 --> 00:08:12,534
AND THAT YOU
SAW THOSE NEW GUNDAMS

148
00:08:12,534 --> 00:08:13,785
IN THE TAKLAMAKAN DESERT.

149
00:08:13,785 --> 00:08:15,537
YEAH.
I SAW THEM ALRIGHT.

150
00:08:15,537 --> 00:08:17,414
YOU ONLY SAW THEM?

151
00:08:17,414 --> 00:08:19,749
AND I HAPPENED TO OVERHEAR
ONE OF THE PILOTS TALKING.

152
00:08:19,749 --> 00:08:20,750
YOU HEARD THEM?

153
00:08:20,750 --> 00:08:22,210
YEAH.

154
00:08:22,210 --> 00:08:24,129
I WAS FLYING MY
REALDO WHEN ALL OF A SUDDEN

155
00:08:24,129 --> 00:08:25,672
ONE OF THOSE GUNDAMS
SHOT ME DOWN.

156
00:08:25,672 --> 00:08:26,881
THEN I STUMBLED
ACROSS IT WHILE

157
00:08:26,881 --> 00:08:28,299
I WAS WAITING TO BE
RESCUED.

158
00:08:28,299 --> 00:08:29,342
(Gasps)

159
00:08:30,635 --> 00:08:31,845
(Determined grunt)

160
00:08:33,555 --> 00:08:34,472
(Hatch opens)

161
00:08:34,472 --> 00:08:35,473
(Gasps)

162
00:08:36,558 --> 00:08:37,934
(Yawning)

163
00:08:37,934 --> 00:08:40,603
HARO...NOTIFY
LAGUNA, PLEASE.

164
00:08:40,603 --> 00:08:42,480
YEAH, I GUESS SO!
YEAH, I GUESS SO!

165
00:08:43,648 --> 00:08:46,151
THE PILOT HAD A HELMET ON
SO I COULDN'T SEE HER FACE...

166
00:08:46,151 --> 00:08:47,736
BUT I COULD TELL IT WAS
A YOUNG GIRL

167
00:08:47,736 --> 00:08:49,988
FROM HER VOICE
AND THE SHAPE OF HER FIGURE.

168
00:08:49,988 --> 00:08:51,197
AND YOU'RE CERTAIN YOU
HEARD HER SAY

169
00:08:51,197 --> 00:08:53,366
THOSE EXACT WORDS,
"NOTIFY LAGUNA"?

170
00:08:53,366 --> 00:08:55,160
I GUESS IT'S POSSIBLE I
MIGHT HAVE MISHEARD HER...

171
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:57,495
ANYWAY, THAT'S ALL THE
INFORMATION I HAVE.

172
00:08:57,495 --> 00:08:58,955
HAVE YOU TOLD THE
MILITARY ABOUT THIS?

173
00:08:58,955 --> 00:09:00,457
NAW, I NEVER FILED
A REPORT ON IT.

174
00:09:00,457 --> 00:09:01,791
(Gulps)

175
00:09:01,791 --> 00:09:03,793
I FIGURED SOMEONE LIKE YOU
WOULD COME ALONG

176
00:09:03,793 --> 00:09:05,545
AND PAY A PRETTY
PRICE FOR THIS INFO.

177
00:09:05,545 --> 00:09:08,256
IT'S A GOOD STORY...CAN I ASK
YOU TO KEEP IT TO YOURSELF

178
00:09:08,256 --> 00:09:09,841
FOR JUST
A LITTLE BIT LONGER?

179
00:09:09,841 --> 00:09:11,551
MY PAYMENT'S GOING TO NEED
TO BE SWEETENED A BIT.

180
00:09:11,551 --> 00:09:14,471
I'LL HAVE SOME MORE CASH
SENT TO YOU IN A FEW DAYS.

181
00:09:14,471 --> 00:09:16,097
APPRECIATE THAT!

182
00:09:16,097 --> 00:09:18,975
MY DAUGHTER'S BIRTHDAY PARTY IS
GOING TO BE EXTRA SPECIAL NOW!

183
00:09:20,894 --> 00:09:25,565
"NOTIFY LAGUNA..."
LAGUNA? IS THAT A NAME?

184
00:09:25,565 --> 00:09:28,485
SOME KIND OF CODEWORD?
IT'S WORTH LOOKING INTO.

185
00:09:33,114 --> 00:09:34,532
FATHER...

186
00:09:34,532 --> 00:09:36,743
LIKE YOU I'M GOING TO LOOK
FOR THE FACTS,

187
00:09:36,743 --> 00:09:38,745
STRING THEM TOGETHER,

188
00:09:38,745 --> 00:09:40,038
AND THEN GET TO
THE TRUTH.

189
00:09:44,375 --> 00:09:46,669
(Humming)

190
00:09:46,669 --> 00:09:47,921
(Tires squeal loudly)

191
00:09:47,921 --> 00:09:48,922
(Gasps)

192
00:09:48,922 --> 00:09:50,215
(Gunshot)

193
00:09:53,384 --> 00:09:59,307
♪

194
00:09:59,307 --> 00:10:00,433
(Laughing)

195
00:10:00,433 --> 00:10:02,227
CONGRATULATIONS!

196
00:10:02,227 --> 00:10:04,270
I WISH YOU BOTH A
LIFE OF HAPPINESS!

197
00:10:04,270 --> 00:10:07,065
THANK YOU, MRS. HALEVY!
FROM BOTH OF US!

198
00:10:07,065 --> 00:10:08,066
(Laughing)

199
00:10:12,153 --> 00:10:14,489
HELLO THERE, SAJI!
HOW YOU DOING?

200
00:10:14,489 --> 00:10:16,908
Saji:
I'M STILL AT WORK. I AGREED
TO TAKE SOME EXTRA SHIFTS

201
00:10:16,908 --> 00:10:18,660
AND NOW I'M EXHAUSTED.
AND YOU?

202
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:20,411
IT'S LIKE THE BEST
WEDDING EVER!

203
00:10:20,411 --> 00:10:23,039
THE BRIDE IS
LIKE ABSOLUTELY BEAUTIFUL!

204
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:24,791
THE FOOD IS OUT
OF THIS WORLD!

205
00:10:24,791 --> 00:10:26,209
AND THEN THERE'S‐‐

206
00:10:26,209 --> 00:10:28,002
HUH? I GOT DISCONNECTED.

207
00:10:28,002 --> 00:10:29,462
AH, IT DOESN'T MATTER.

208
00:10:29,462 --> 00:10:32,131
I'VE ALMOST REACHED
MY SAVINGS GOAL!

209
00:10:32,131 --> 00:10:33,174
(Yawning)

210
00:10:33,174 --> 00:10:34,634
JUST A LITTLE LONGER!

211
00:10:35,385 --> 00:10:36,594
HEY, DELIVERY BOY!

212
00:10:36,594 --> 00:10:38,721
ALRIGHT!

213
00:10:38,721 --> 00:10:40,932
SAJI? SAJI!

214
00:10:40,932 --> 00:10:42,934
AW, WHAT IS THIS?

215
00:10:42,934 --> 00:10:43,935
HMM?

216
00:10:45,103 --> 00:10:48,356
I WONDER IF THOSE
LIGHTS UP THERE ARE...

217
00:10:48,356 --> 00:10:49,858
GUNDAMS!

218
00:10:49,858 --> 00:10:50,859
OH, WOW!

219
00:10:50,859 --> 00:10:52,861
I'VE NEVER SEEN THEM FOR REAL!

220
00:10:54,070 --> 00:10:56,114
Johann:
LAGUNA HAS JUST SENT US OUR
LATEST MISSION.

221
00:10:56,114 --> 00:10:57,323
PROCEED TO
THE TARGET POINT.

222
00:10:57,323 --> 00:10:58,867
Michael:
WHAT, ANOTHER ONE?

223
00:10:58,867 --> 00:11:02,662
I DON'T WANT TO! WE'VE BEEN
WORKING NON‐STOP LATELY!

224
00:11:02,662 --> 00:11:06,082
Johann:
HANG IN THERE. WE'RE DOING
THIS TO ERADICATE WAR.

225
00:11:06,833 --> 00:11:08,668
OH, DARN IT!

226
00:11:08,668 --> 00:11:09,669
HUH?

227
00:11:12,463 --> 00:11:13,798
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

228
00:11:13,798 --> 00:11:16,342
WE'RE TOTALLY WORKING OUR
BUTTS OFF...

229
00:11:16,342 --> 00:11:18,511
AND THEY'RE
LAUGHING AND HAVING A PARTY!

230
00:11:18,511 --> 00:11:20,471
YOU GUYS JUST DON'T
GET IT, DO YOU?

231
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,893
I THINK YOUR WORLD
IS ABOUT TO CHANGE.

232
00:11:26,394 --> 00:11:27,645
(Laughing)

233
00:11:27,645 --> 00:11:28,980
HEY, WHAT'S THAT?

234
