HUH?

235
00:11:29,981 --> 00:11:31,107
A MOBILE SUIT?

236
00:11:31,107 --> 00:11:32,191
ISN'T THAT A GUNDAM?

237
00:11:33,902 --> 00:11:35,236
A GUNDAM...

238
00:11:37,739 --> 00:11:38,907
WHAT?

239
00:11:39,657 --> 00:11:41,451
YOU'RE BETTER OFF DEAD.

240
00:11:41,451 --> 00:11:42,535
(Blast)

241
00:11:42,535 --> 00:11:45,038
(Boom)

242
00:11:45,538 --> 00:11:46,289
(Screaming)

243
00:11:53,588 --> 00:11:55,006
(Gasps)

244
00:11:58,718 --> 00:12:00,094
(People coughing)

245
00:12:01,220 --> 00:12:03,222
MY DAD...

246
00:12:03,222 --> 00:12:05,433
MY MOM...

247
00:12:05,433 --> 00:12:07,393
(Gasping)

248
00:12:07,393 --> 00:12:09,938
DAD! MOM!

249
00:12:09,938 --> 00:12:11,356
(Boom)

250
00:12:11,356 --> 00:12:12,315
(Screaming)

251
00:12:15,193 --> 00:12:17,111
NENA, WHAT DO YOU
THINK YOU'RE DOING?

252
00:12:17,111 --> 00:12:19,447
SORRY, I MUST HAVE HIT THE
WRONG SWITCH OR SOMETHING!

253
00:12:19,447 --> 00:12:21,658
YOU'RE PROBABLY JUST TIRED
FROM ALL THESE MISSIONS.

254
00:12:21,658 --> 00:12:23,284
DON'T GO OFF
ON YOUR OWN, NENA.

255
00:12:23,284 --> 00:12:25,036
OKAY!

256
00:12:25,036 --> 00:12:26,329
(Giggles)

257
00:12:30,416 --> 00:12:36,005
♪

258
00:12:37,215 --> 00:12:40,510
(Humming)

259
00:12:45,014 --> 00:12:47,183
TEAM TRINITY LAUNCHED AN
ATTACK ON CIVILIANS?

260
00:12:47,183 --> 00:12:49,102
WHAT WERE THEY THINKING?

261
00:12:49,102 --> 00:12:50,937
MAYBE THEY WERE TARGETING
SOMEBODY WHO WAS GUILTY

262
00:12:50,937 --> 00:12:52,230
OF PROMOTING WAR.

263
00:12:52,230 --> 00:12:54,190
BUT IT DOESN'T LOOK
LIKE THAT'S THE CASE HERE.

264
00:12:54,190 --> 00:12:55,984
THERE'S NOTHING ABOUT IT IN
THE MISSION DATA

265
00:12:55,984 --> 00:12:58,861
TRINITY ENTERED
INTO VEDA.

266
00:12:58,861 --> 00:13:01,155
THEY ATTACKED THOSE PEOPLE
FOR NO REASON AT ALL...

267
00:13:01,155 --> 00:13:02,532
BUT THAT'S JUST...

268
00:13:02,532 --> 00:13:03,616
(Bang)

269
00:13:03,616 --> 00:13:05,034
WHAT THE HELL ARE THOSE BASTARDS
DOING?

270
00:13:05,034 --> 00:13:06,327
ARE THEY PLAYING
GAMES?

271
00:13:08,621 --> 00:13:10,915
AN ATTACK ON CIVILIANS...

272
00:13:10,915 --> 00:13:12,458
BY A GUNDAM.

273
00:13:15,211 --> 00:13:17,046
Student #18A:
TERRORISTS AGAIN?

274
00:13:17,046 --> 00:13:18,923
IT SAYS MOBILE SUITS
WERE INVOLVED...

275
00:13:18,923 --> 00:13:20,425
IT'S PROBABLY
THOSE GUNDAMS.

276
00:13:20,425 --> 00:13:22,218
(Phone ringing)

277
00:13:22,218 --> 00:13:24,846
Operator:
THE NUMBER YOU HAVE
DIALED IS NOT IN SERVICE.

278
00:13:24,846 --> 00:13:26,639
I WONDER WHAT'S GOING ON?

279
00:13:26,639 --> 00:13:29,517
MAYBE HER PARENTS ARE
KEEPING HER FROM ANSWERING.

280
00:13:29,517 --> 00:13:32,437
LOUISE HALEVY, THE FOREIGN
EXCHANGE STUDENT?

281
00:13:32,437 --> 00:13:35,189
YES. SHE HASN'T BEEN TO
SCHOOL IN THREE DAYS.

282
00:13:35,189 --> 00:13:36,858
IS SHE YOUR GIRLFRIEND?

283
00:13:36,858 --> 00:13:38,443
UH, YEAH...

284
00:13:38,443 --> 00:13:40,278
(Laughing)

285
00:13:40,278 --> 00:13:41,612
JUST GIVE ME
A MOMENT.

286
00:13:41,612 --> 00:13:42,655
(Chuckling)

287
00:13:42,655 --> 00:13:43,948
(Gasps)

288
00:13:43,948 --> 00:13:45,742
IS THERE SOMETHING WRONG?

289
00:13:45,742 --> 00:13:48,286
IT LOOKS LIKE MISS HALEVY
WAS INVOLVED IN AN ACCIDENT

290
00:13:48,286 --> 00:13:50,329
IN SPAIN AND HAS BEEN
ADMITTED TO THE HOSPITAL.

291
00:13:50,329 --> 00:13:52,457
WHAT KIND OF ACCIDENT
WAS SHE IN?

292
00:13:52,457 --> 00:13:54,959
I DON'T REALLY KNOW, ALL
WE HAVE IS A NOTIFICATION

293
00:13:54,959 --> 00:13:56,627
OF A LEAVE OF ABSENCE.

294
00:13:56,627 --> 00:13:58,463
PLEASE MISS, I NEED THE
NAME OF THE HOSPITAL!

295
00:13:58,463 --> 00:13:59,630
(Engine running)

296
00:14:04,177 --> 00:14:05,970
HUH?

297
00:14:05,970 --> 00:14:08,806
A SPANISH HOLIDAY RESORT...FROM
STATEMENTS BY SURVIVORS,

298
00:14:08,806 --> 00:14:11,267
IT'S KNOWN THE ATTACK
WAS CARRIED OUT BY A GUNDAM...

299
00:14:11,267 --> 00:14:12,351
(Gasping)

300
00:14:12,351 --> 00:14:14,145
BUT WHY?

301
00:14:19,358 --> 00:14:21,360
(Footsteps echo)

302
00:14:24,405 --> 00:14:25,615
HEY THERE...

303
00:14:25,615 --> 00:14:27,408
WHAT BRINGS YOU OUT HERE
THIS TIME OF NIGHT?

304
00:14:27,408 --> 00:14:29,410
KATAGIRI!
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

305
00:14:29,410 --> 00:14:31,329
YOU'RE SUPPOSED TO BE
IN A HOSPITAL BED!

306
00:14:31,329 --> 00:14:33,039
WITHOUT ME YOU'D NEVER
BE ABLE TO MAINTAIN THIS

307
00:14:33,039 --> 00:14:34,707
CUSTOM FLAG OF YOURS.

308
00:14:34,707 --> 00:14:37,001
AFTER ALL THESE ARE MACHINES
THAT WERE TUNED BY

309
00:14:37,001 --> 00:14:38,419
THE GREAT
PROFESSOR EIFMAN HIMSELF.

310
00:14:38,419 --> 00:14:39,629
(Cries out)

311
00:14:43,841 --> 00:14:45,343
DON'T PUSH YOURSELF,
OLD FRIEND.

312
00:14:45,343 --> 00:14:46,385
I HAVE TO.

313
00:14:46,385 --> 00:14:47,720
HUH?

314
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:49,931
JUST LIKE YOU WON'T
COMPROMISE ON SOME THINGS...

315
00:14:49,931 --> 00:14:52,183
THERE ARE SOME THINGS I
WON'T COMPROMISE ON.

316
00:14:53,810 --> 00:14:54,811
(Laughs)

317
00:14:54,811 --> 00:14:56,938
YOU ARE SO
DAMN STUBBORN.

318
00:14:56,938 --> 00:14:58,481
NOT AS MUCH
AS YOU ARE.

319
00:15:01,442 --> 00:15:03,861
Katagiri:
I'VE BEEN THINKING
ABOUT THIS...

320
00:15:03,861 --> 00:15:07,156
THE GUNDAMS ATTACKED OVER FLAG
HEADQUARTERS FOR ONE REASON...

321
00:15:07,156 --> 00:15:09,867
AND THAT WAS TO
GET PROFESSOR EIFMAN.

322
00:15:09,867 --> 00:15:11,202
HOW DO YOU FIGURE?

323
00:15:11,202 --> 00:15:13,454
THE PROFESSOR WAS ON THE VERGE
OF FIGURING OUT

324
00:15:13,454 --> 00:15:15,706
THE TRUE NATURE
OF THE GUNDAMS' ENERGY SYSTEMS

325
00:15:15,706 --> 00:15:17,458
AND THEIR SPECIAL
PARTICLES.

326
00:15:17,458 --> 00:15:20,878
SOMEHOW CELESTIAL BEING MUST
HAVE FOUND OUT ABOUT THIS.

327
00:15:20,878 --> 00:15:22,296
SO THEY KILLED HIM

328
00:15:22,296 --> 00:15:23,965
WHILE MAKING IT
LOOK LIKE AN ARMED INTERVENTION.

329
00:15:23,965 --> 00:15:25,216
HMM.

330
00:15:25,216 --> 00:15:27,385
YOU THINK THERE'S A
SPY IN OUR MILITARY?

331
00:15:27,385 --> 00:15:29,303
IT WOULD BE UNREALISTIC TO
THINK THAT THERE WASN'T ONE.

332
00:15:29,303 --> 00:15:31,389
HMM.

333
00:15:31,389 --> 00:15:35,852
(Alarm Sounding):
DETECTING A POSSIBLE GUNDAM AT
POINT F‐ 3988 OVER IOWA!

334
00:15:35,852 --> 00:15:37,186
THEY'VE SPOTTED A GUNDAM!

335
00:15:37,186 --> 00:15:39,438
THERE'S ONLY ONE POSSIBLE
TARGET AT THAT POINT...

336
00:15:39,438 --> 00:15:40,481
(Gasps)

337
00:15:40,481 --> 00:15:42,150
IRIS CORPORATION'S
MUNITIONS PLANT!

338
00:15:42,150 --> 00:15:45,153
IT CAN'T BE! IT MAY BE A
WEAPONS FACTORY

339
00:15:45,153 --> 00:15:47,155
BUT THE WORKERS
THERE ARE ALL CIVILIANS!

340
00:15:47,947 --> 00:15:50,199
IS MY FLAG
READY FOR LAUNCH?

341
00:15:51,450 --> 00:15:53,536
(Over radio):
THIS IS GRAHAM!
I'M TAKING THE LEAD!

342
00:15:53,536 --> 00:15:55,329
Katagiri:
HEADING OUT ALONE
IS JUST RECKLESS!

343
00:15:57,206 --> 00:16:00,168
SOUNDS REASONABLE, TOO BAD
I'M AN UNREASONABLE MAN!

344
00:16:02,170 --> 00:16:03,171
(Screaming)

345
00:16:03,171 --> 00:16:04,338
(Siren wailing)

346
00:16:04,338 --> 00:16:05,548
(Boom)

347
00:16:13,097 --> 00:16:14,390
HUH?

348
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:16,100
AN INCOMING MACHINE.

349
00:16:16,100 --> 00:16:17,768
AND IT'S A FAST ONE...

350
00:16:20,021 --> 00:16:21,606
SO IT IS ONE OF THE
NEW ONES!

351
00:16:21,606 --> 00:16:23,858
(Rapid blasting)

352
00:16:28,404 --> 00:16:29,697
HE'S GOOD!

353
00:16:29,697 --> 00:16:31,657
I DON'T CARE HOW MUCH
BETTER YOUR MACHINE IS!

354
00:16:33,868 --> 00:16:35,328
TODAY I AM BEYOND THAT!

355
00:16:36,871 --> 00:16:38,831
I STRIKE LIKE AN
AVENGING ANGEL!

356
00:16:40,374 --> 00:16:41,292
WHAT THE...

357
00:16:51,802 --> 00:16:54,138
THAT'S...IMPOSSIBLE!

358
00:16:58,809 --> 00:17:00,269
(Gasping)

359
00:17:00,269 --> 00:17:03,481
THAT WAS FOR YOU, HOWARD.
SOME PAY BACK.

360
00:17:03,481 --> 00:17:05,024
(Vomiting)

361
00:17:05,024 --> 00:17:07,068
(Gasping)

362
00:17:07,068 --> 00:17:10,696
MY BODY CAN'T TAKE
THIS MANY G'S!

363
00:17:12,281 --> 00:17:14,951
(Waves washing on shore)

364
00:17:14,951 --> 00:17:16,160
Lockon:
SETSUNA!

365
00:17:17,078 --> 00:17:19,413
IT'S TEAM TRINITY.
THEY WENT AND DID IT AGAIN.

366
00:17:19,413 --> 00:17:20,498
DID WHAT?

367
00:17:20,498 --> 00:17:23,459
THEY HIT AN
IRIS CORPORATION FACTORY.

368
00:17:23,459 --> 00:17:24,919
OVER EIGHT HUNDRED PEOPLE
DIED IN THE ATTACK.

369
00:17:24,919 --> 00:17:26,170
(Gasps)

370
00:17:26,170 --> 00:17:28,214
ALL THE WORKERS IN THAT
FACTORY WERE CIVILIANS.

371
00:17:28,214 --> 00:17:30,633
IT'S NO BETTER THAN
INDISCRIMINATE TERRORISM!

372
00:17:30,633 --> 00:17:31,634
(Setsuna running)

373
00:17:31,634 --> 00:17:32,635
HUH?

374
00:17:32,635 --> 00:17:34,178
SETSUNA!

375
00:17:35,012 --> 00:17:36,430
(Sumeragi thinking):
VEDA...

376
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:38,224
THE QUANTUM COMPUTER
PROCESSING SYSTEM

377
00:17:38,224 --> 00:17:40,518
THAT'S THE BACKBONE
OF OUR OPERATION PLAN.

378
00:17:42,019 --> 00:17:43,479
IN THE OFF‐CHANCE THAT
SOMEONE...

379
00:17:43,479 --> 00:17:46,899
HAS ACTUALLY HACKED VEDA,

380
00:17:46,899 --> 00:17:48,567
WE'RE JUST GOING
TO HAVE TO FIND SOME WAY

381
00:17:48,567 --> 00:17:50,486
TO CONTINUE OUR MISSIONS
WITHOUT IT.

382
00:17:51,445 --> 00:17:54,031
THERE IS
NO WAY WE CAN DO IT.

383
00:17:54,615 --> 00:17:55,616
(Beeping)

384
00:17:55,616 --> 00:17:56,617
HUH?

385
00:17:58,244 --> 00:18:00,288
IT'S FROM BILLY...

386
00:18:00,288 --> 00:18:01,289
(Gasps)

387
00:18:01,289 --> 00:18:02,873
NO, PROFESSOR EIFMAN
WAS KILLED!

388
00:18:02,873 --> 00:18:05,459
AND IT WAS IN AN
ATTACK BY GUNDAMS.

389
00:18:05,459 --> 00:18:07,211
THERE'S A PROBLEM,
MISS SUMERAGI!

390
00:18:07,211 --> 00:18:08,879
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

391
00:18:09,839 --> 00:18:11,465
LOUISE WAS HURT?

392
00:18:11,465 --> 00:18:14,051
AND HE'S GOING TO
SPAIN TO BE WITH HER?

393
00:18:18,055 --> 00:18:19,056
SAJI...

394
00:18:22,643 --> 00:18:23,853
(Car zooms by)

395
00:18:24,437 --> 00:18:25,980
(Screeches to a halt)

396
00:18:26,522 --> 00:18:27,982
(Panting)

397
00:18:32,903 --> 00:18:33,904
(Panting)

398
00:18:34,613 --> 00:18:35,865
HEY, YOU!

399
00:18:35,865 --> 00:18:37,450
NO RUNNING IN THE HALLWAY!

400
00:18:37,450 --> 00:18:39,368
(Saji panting)

401
00:18:39,368 --> 00:18:41,454
(Catching breath)

402
00:18:45,916 --> 00:18:47,626
LOUISE?

403
00:18:47,626 --> 00:18:49,754
SAJI... WHY ARE YOU HERE?

404
00:18:51,505 --> 00:18:53,007
(Sighs)

405
00:18:53,007 --> 00:18:55,092
I HEARD YOU
WERE IN AN ACCIDENT.

406
00:18:55,092 --> 00:18:57,470
SORRY IT TOOK ME SO
LONG TO GET HERE.

407
00:18:57,470 --> 00:18:59,013
BUT YOU'RE
SKIPPING SCHOOL.

408
00:18:59,013 --> 00:19:00,306
AW, DON'T WORRY.

409
00:19:00,306 --> 00:19:02,892
BUT WHAT A RELIEF...
YOU SEEM WELL.

410
00:19:02,892 --> 00:19:05,353
THANK GOD FOR THAT.

411
00:19:05,353 --> 00:19:08,898
OH, THAT'S RIGHT! I'VE GOT
SOMETHING FOR YOU, LOUISE...

412
00:19:08,898 --> 00:19:10,649
IT'S RIGHT HERE...

413
00:19:10,649 --> 00:19:11,859
WHAT'S THAT?

414
00:19:14,362 --> 00:19:15,363
(Gasps)

415
00:19:15,363 --> 00:19:16,572
FOR ME?

416
00:19:16,572 --> 00:19:17,823
(Chuckling)

417
00:19:17,823 --> 00:19:20,451
IT'S THAT SET OF RINGS YOU
WANTED A WHILE BACK!

418
00:19:20,451 --> 00:19:23,037
I WORKED LIKE CRAZY DURING
THE WHOLE EXAM BREAK...

419
00:19:23,037 --> 00:19:24,747
AND I MADE
ENOUGH TO BUY THEM!

420
00:19:24,747 --> 00:19:26,999
THEY'RE FOR YOU...
LOUISE!

421
00:19:33,255 --> 00:19:35,007
IT'S BEAUTIFUL...

422
00:19:37,385 --> 00:19:38,552
(Nervous chuckle)

423
00:19:39,929 --> 00:19:43,766
UH LOUISE...I HAVE SOMETHING
I HAVE TO TELL YOU...

424
00:19:43,766 --> 00:19:44,809
SEE, THE MORE I
THINK OF YOU‐‐

425
00:19:44,809 --> 00:19:46,852
I'M SO... SORRY.

426
00:19:46,852 --> 00:19:48,104
HUH?

427
00:19:48,104 --> 00:19:50,481
YOU WENT TO THE TROUBLE
OF BUYING THESE...

428
00:19:50,481 --> 00:19:52,274
AND THEY'RE SO
BEAUTIFUL...

429
00:19:58,864 --> 00:20:01,075
BUT I CAN'T
WEAR THIS RING.

430
00:20:05,663 --> 00:20:06,664
UH...

431
00:20:08,666 --> 00:20:10,626
I CAN'T WEAR THIS RING.

432
00:20:10,626 --> 00:20:11,919
(Gasps)

433
00:20:11,919 --> 00:20:14,797
OH, NO, LOUISE...
YOU MEAN...

434
00:20:14,797 --> 00:20:17,049
(Sobbing)

435
00:20:17,049 --> 00:20:20,136
I REALLY AM...
SORRY.

436
00:20:22,304 --> 00:20:27,059
(Weeping)

437
00:20:35,734 --> 00:20:37,736
(Gasps)

438
00:20:37,736 --> 00:20:40,322
Nurse:
LOUISE'S PARENTS, ALONG
WITH ALL OF HER RELATIVES,

439
00:20:40,322 --> 00:20:42,158
WERE LOST
IN THE ACCIDENT.

440
00:20:42,158 --> 00:20:43,325
DON'T UPSET HER.

441
00:20:46,454 --> 00:20:50,082
Nurse #18C:
I KNOW THEY WANT TO ELIMINATE
WAR OR SOMETHING LIKE THAT,

442
00:20:50,082 --> 00:20:52,418
BUT WHEN THEY
FIGHT PEOPLE GET HURT.

443
00:20:52,418 --> 00:20:54,044
WE'LL DO OUR BEST TO
HEAL THEIR INJURIES...

444
00:20:54,044 --> 00:20:56,589
BUT WE CAN'T
HEAL THEIR HEARTS.

445
00:20:56,589 --> 00:20:59,425
Nurse #18D:
WHAT? BUT THE HALEVYS
WERE RICH AND FAMOUS!

446
00:20:59,425 --> 00:21:01,343
Nurse #18E:
THE FAMILY WAS
ATTACKED BY A GUNDAM!

447
00:21:01,343 --> 00:21:03,012
THE WHOLE FAMILY'S GONE!

448
00:21:03,012 --> 00:21:04,513
Nurse #18F:
HOW AWFUL...

449
00:21:04,513 --> 00:21:06,265
Nurse #18G:
MAYBE THE FAMILY WAS
PROMOTING WAR...

450
00:21:06,265 --> 00:21:08,559
Nurse #18F:
BUT THEY WERE CIVILIANS!

451
00:21:08,559 --> 00:21:11,395
Nurse #18E:
IN THE END, IT JUST
MEANS MORE WORK FOR US.

452
00:21:17,193 --> 00:21:18,152
(Sighs)

453
00:21:25,034 --> 00:21:26,202
(Sobs)

454
00:21:26,202 --> 00:21:27,536
OH, LOUISE...

455
00:21:27,536 --> 00:21:32,374
(Weeping)

456
00:21:36,462 --> 00:21:38,297
Michael:
I NEVER THOUGHT THERE
WAS SOMEBODY OUT THERE

457
00:21:38,297 --> 00:21:39,840
WHO COULD ACTUALLY
GIVE YOU TROUBLE.

458
00:21:39,840 --> 00:21:41,342
Nena:
CARELESSNESS
IS THE REAL ENEMY.

459
00:21:41,342 --> 00:21:43,260
I'M JUST GOING TO HAVE TO
TAKE THAT TO HEART.

460
00:21:43,260 --> 00:21:44,261
HUH?

461
00:21:45,471 --> 00:21:46,472
WHAT THE...

462
00:21:46,472 --> 00:21:47,473
THOSE ARE PARTICLE BEAMS!

463
00:21:47,473 --> 00:21:48,474
(Grunting)

464
00:21:48,474 --> 00:21:49,433
A GUNDAM!

465
00:21:51,727 --> 00:21:53,729
Johann:
IT'S THE GUNDAM EXIA!

466
00:21:53,729 --> 00:21:55,940
EXIA HAS LOCATED THE TARGETS.

467
00:21:55,940 --> 00:21:58,859
HAVE CONCLUDED THE THREE
GUNDAM THRONE UNITS

468
00:21:58,859 --> 00:22:00,653
ARE GUILTY
OF PROMOTING CONFLICT.

469
00:22:00,653 --> 00:22:03,614
COMMENCING ARMED
INTERVENTION.

470
00:22:03,614 --> 00:22:06,492
EXIA...
WILL ELIMINATE TARGETS!

471
00:22:11,580 --> 00:22:21,632
♪

472
00:22:21,632 --> 00:22:41,652
♪

473
00:22:41,652 --> 00:23:01,672
♪

474
00:23:01,672 --> 00:23:21,692
♪

475
00:23:21,692 --> 00:23:41,295
♪

476
00:23:43,839 --> 00:23:45,883
Narrator:
THE ONE HE WISHED
VENGEANCE UPON

477
00:23:45,883 --> 00:23:47,926
WAS RIGHT THERE
BESIDE HIM.

478
00:23:47,926 --> 00:23:49,928
WHEN HE LEARNS THIS,
LOCKON GATHERS HIS ANGER

479
00:23:49,928 --> 00:23:52,306
AND AIMS HIS WEAPON.

